flowchart TD
    A[User action] --> B{Excel readable?}
    B -- no --> B1[Friendly Excel error + log detail]
    B -- yes --> C{Records selected?}
    C -- no --> C1[Do not print / ask for selection]
    C -- yes --> D[Preview approval]
    D --> E{Driver SATO WS408 installed?}
    E -- no --> E1[Install/contact IT guidance]
    E -- yes --> F{QPainter begins print job?}
    F -- no --> F1[Show print startup error]
    F -- yes --> G[Print labels]
